Enum FSUIPCWrapper.FSUIPCResult

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<FSUIPCWrapper.FSUIPCResult>
com.mouseviator.fsuipc.FSUIPCWrapper.FSUIPCResult

Enclosing class:
FSUIPCWrapper
public static enum FSUIPCWrapper.FSUIPCResult
extends java.lang.Enum<FSUIPCWrapper.FSUIPCResult>
An enumeration of known result codes, that can be returned by calls to FSUIPCWrapper.read(int, int, byte[]), FSUIPCWrapper.write(int, int, byte[]), FSUIPCWrapper.process(). Use FSUIPCWrapper.getResult() to get the last result value.
